OL,3,CMeet the volunteers at Cafe Lingo
OL,4,Chelping newcomers integrate into the
OL,5,Cisland
OL,7,FVolunteers on the Isle of Man are
OL,8,Fcelebrating ten years of helping
OL,9,Fnewcomers integrate into the Isle of
OL,10,FMan.
OL,12,FCafe Lingo offers free weekly lessons
OL,13,Fto anyone wishing to learn English,
OL,14,Fwho may have moved to the island from
OL,15,Fa foreign country.
OL,17,FSylvie Geal-Wilkes is one of the
OL,18,Fteachers giving the weekly classes,
OL,19,Fand said the aim was to 'give people a
OL,20,Fplace where they felt they belonged'.
OL,26,@kD@[rrtD@Drr
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
