PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773144740
OL,3,CMeet the volunteers at Cafe Lingo
OL,4,Chelping newcomers integrate into the
OL,5,Cisland
OL,7,FShe said: "Us who've lived here for a
OL,8,Flong time, I think we underestimate
OL,9,Fthe cultural differences. Our constant
OL,10,Fhabit of thanking everyone,
OL,11,Fapologising to everyone, thanking
OL,12,Fstrangers. It's so totally different."
OL,14,FMore than 550 'students' have attended
OL,15,Fthe classes in the last decade, with a
OL,16,Fnoticeable increase due to conflicts
OL,17,Facross the world.
OL,26,@kD@[rr
