CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773144740
OL,3,CMeet the volunteers at Cafe Lingo
OL,4,Chelping newcomers integrate into the
OL,5,Cisland
OL,7,FOksana Fedorovych moved to the island
OL,8,Ffrom Ukraine with her husband eight
OL,9,Fyears ago, and said it was 'stressful'
OL,10,Fto live in a place so unknown to her.
OL,12,FHowever, a year later she joined Cafe
OL,13,FLingo.
OL,15,FShe said: "From the first lesson, I
OL,16,Fdecided for myself I should be here
OL,17,Fbecause of the absolutely amazing
OL,18,Fatmosphere, incredible volunteers -
OL,19,Fyou can feel yourself here.
OL,26,@kD@[rrtD@err
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
