PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773144740
OL,3,CMeet the volunteers at Cafe Lingo
OL,4,Chelping newcomers integrate into the
OL,5,Cisland
OL,7,FFollowing the Russian invasion of
OL,8,FUkraine in 2022, a large number of
OL,9,Frefugees were welcomed to the Isle of
OL,10,FMan.
OL,12,FOksana was then asked whether she
OL,13,Fwould become a teacher during this
OL,14,Ftime, and became invaluable to the
OL,15,Fvolunteers welcoming Ukrainian people
OL,16,Fto the group.
OL,26,@kD@[rr
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
