CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773144740
OL,3,CMeet the volunteers at Cafe Lingo
OL,4,Chelping newcomers integrate into the
OL,5,Cisland
OL,7,F"When the Ukrainians came to Cafe
OL,8,FLingo, I tried to do my best and all
OL,9,Fvolunteers, I really am grateful to
OL,10,Fall the volunteers how they were
OL,11,Fsupporting the Ukrainians."
OL,13,FOne of those who travelled to the
OL,14,Fisland to flee the conflict was Yulia
OL,15,FBrykailo, who moved to the island with
OL,16,Fher children.
OL,18,FSince attending the group, Yulia then
OL,19,Fwrote and illustrated a children's
OL,20,Fbook, inspired by her daughter while
OL,21,Fshe adjusted to life on the island.
OL,26,@kD@[rroD@arr
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
