PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773144740
OL,3,CMeet the volunteers at Cafe Lingo
OL,4,Chelping newcomers integrate into the
OL,5,Cisland
OL,7,F"My children and I, came to Cafe Lingo
OL,8,Fevery Saturday because it's a place
OL,9,Fwhere you can find friends, some
OL,10,Fsnacks, get creative.
OL,12,FWhen asked about her inspiration for
OL,13,Fthe book, she spoke fondly of the
OL,14,Fcommunity at the language class.
OL,16,F"One part that's very important is
OL,17,FCafe Lingo, because she finds friends
OL,18,Fand found information where she can
OL,19,Ffind some treasure on the Isle of Man."
OL,26,@kD@[rryD@Drr
