OL,3,CMeet the volunteers at Cafe Lingo
OL,4,Chelping newcomers integrate into the
OL,5,Cisland
OL,7,FCafe Lingo was founded in 2016 by
OL,8,FKaren Norton, after she noticed an
OL,9,Fincrease in the number of foreign
OL,10,Fspeakers to the island.
OL,12,FShe said: "Being a Manxie, I
OL,13,Funderstand that a lot of information
OL,14,Fis assumed, but in actual fact when
OL,15,Fyou come here from a foreign place,
OL,16,Fnot everything is obvious.
OL,18,F"I couldn't lose the idea, really,
OL,19,Fthat there was something I could do
OL,20,Fabout it to help the people, to learn
OL,21,FEnglish and help allay fears."
OL,26,@kD@[rroD@Drr
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
