CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773144740
OL,3,CMeet the volunteers at Cafe Lingo
OL,4,Chelping newcomers integrate into the
OL,5,Cisland
OL,7,FA decade on, the team are celebrating
OL,8,Ftheir 10th anniversary, building on
OL,9,Fthe foundations of inclusivity on the
OL,10,Fisle of Man.
OL,12,FTheir weekly classes continue every
OL,13,FSaturday for anyone interested in
OL,14,Fattending, with more information
OL,15,Favailable on their Facebook page.
OL,26,@kD@[rr
